model_group.name: Modeling group
model_group.description: Properties of different types are separated into different modeling groups for analysis

land_area_sqft.name: Land area in square feet
land_area_sqft.description: Land area in square feet. If the value given by the locality is missing, this is filled in from the GIS value.

land_area_given_sqft.name: Land area in square feet
land_area_given_sqft.description: Land area in square feet. This value is the original unaltered value given by the locality.

land_area_gis_sqft.name: Land area (GIS) in square feet
land_area_gis_sqft.description: Land area in square feet as automatically calculated by GIS

land_area_gis_delta_sqft.name: Land area GIS difference in square feet
land_area_gis_delta_sqft.description: Difference between the land area as given by {jurisdiction} and the land area as automatically calculated by GIS

land_area_gis_delta_percent.name: Percent delta land area
land_area_gis_delta_percent.description: Percent difference between the land area as given by {jurisdiction} and the land area as automatically calculated by GIS

floor_area_ratio.name: Floor area ratio
floor_area_ratio.description: Ratio between the total floor area of the building(s) on the parcel and the size of the parcel

land_area_delta_from_median_sqft.name: Land area delta from median
land_area_delta_from_median_sqft.description: Difference between the land area of the parcel and the median land area in the jurisdiction

geom_rectangularity_num.name: Rectangularity (numeric)
geom_rectangularity_num.description: How rectangular the parcel is, expressed as a numeric value (1.0 is a perfect rectangle)

geom_rectangularity_txt.name: Rectangularity (text)
geom_rectangularity_txt.description: How rectangular the parcel is, expressed as a text value

geom_vertices.name: Number of vertices
geom_vertices.description: Number of vertices in the parcel's simplified polygon

geom_aspect_ratio.name: Aspect ratio
geom_aspect_ratio.description: Aspect ratio of the parcel (width divided by height)

is_geom_triangular.name: Is triangular
is_geom_triangular.description: Whether the parcel is triangular in shape

is_geom_complex.name: Is complex geometry
is_geom_complex.description: Whether the parcel has complex geometry

is_geom_irregular.name: Is irregular
is_geom_irregular.description: Whether the parcel is irregular in shape

risk_disaster.name: Disaster risk
risk_disaster.description: Disaster risk (FEMA National Risk Index rating)

is_opportunity_zone.name: Opportunity zone
is_opportunity_zone.description: Whether the parcel is in a Federal Qualified Opportunity Zone

dist_to_cbd.name: Distance to central business district
dist_to_cbd.description: Distance to the central business district

dist_to_greenspace.name: Distance to greenspace
dist_to_greenspace.description: Distance to the nearest greenspace (e.g., park)

address.name: Address
address.description: Street address of the parcel (situs location)

is_usps_vacant.name: USPS vacancy indicator
is_usps_vacant.description: Whether the USPS has flagged the address as vacant (not as in vacant land, but as in not receiving mail, e.g., a likely vacant building, seasonal property, etc.)

mail_address.name: Mail address
mail_address.description: Mailing address where tax/assessment info is sent

bldg_count.name: Building count
bldg_count.description: Number of buildings on the parcel

model_land_alloc.name: Model land allocation
model_land_alloc.description: Model estimate of what % of the total value of the parcel is due to the land value alone

model_market_value_land_sqft.name: Model market value per land square foot
model_market_value_land_sqft.description: Model market value, divided by the size of the parcel

model_land_value_land_sqft.name: Model land value per land square foot
model_land_value_land_sqft.description: Model land value, divided by the size of the parcel

assr_land_alloc.name: {jurisdiction} land allocation
assr_land_alloc.description: {jurisdiction}'s estimate of what % of the total value of the parcel is due to the land value alone

assr_market_value_land_sqft.name: {jurisdiction} market value per land square foot
assr_market_value_land_sqft.description: {jurisdiction} market value, divided by the size of the parcel

assr_land_value_land_sqft.name: {jurisdiction} land value per land square foot
assr_land_value_land_sqft.description: {jurisdiction} land value, divided by the size of the parcel

true_land_value.name: True land value
true_land_value.description: Ground truth land value (only defined for synthetic data models)

true_impr_value.name: True improvement value
true_impr_value.description: Ground truth improvement value (only defined for synthetic data models)

true_market_value.name: True market value
true_market_value.description: Ground truth market value (only defined for synthetic data models)

true_land_alloc.name: True land allocation
true_land_alloc.description: Ground truth % of the total value of the parcel is due to the land value alone (only defined for synthetic data models)

true_market_value_land_sqft.name: True market value per land square foot
true_market_value_land_sqft.description: True market value, divided by the size of the parcel (only defined for synthetic data models)

true_land_value_land_sqft.name: True land value per land square foot
true_land_value_land_sqft.description: True land value, divided by the size of the parcel (only defined for synthetic data models)

bldg_units.name: Building units
bldg_units.description: Number of units in the building

osm_bldg_area_footprint_sqft.name: Building area (footprint) in square feet (OSM)
osm_bldg_area_footprint_sqft.description: Building area (footprint) in square feet (from Open Street Map)

bldg_stories.name: Building stories
bldg_stories.description: Number of stories in the building

bldg_rooms_bed.name: Bedrooms
bldg_rooms_bed.description: Number of bedrooms in the building

bldg_rooms_bath.name: Bathrooms
bldg_rooms_bath.description: Number of bathrooms in the building

bldg_rooms_bath_full.name: Full baths
bldg_rooms_bath_full.description: Number of full bathrooms in the building

bldg_rooms_bath_half.name: Half baths
bldg_rooms_bath_half.description: Number of half-bathrooms in the building

vacant_sale.name: Vacant sale
vacant_sale.description: Whether the sale was for a vacant parcel

elevation_stdev.name: Elevation change
elevation_stdev.description: Change in elevation across the parcel (standard deviation)

slope_mean.name: Slope
slope_mean.description: Mean slope across the parcel (in degrees)

slope_stdev.name: Slope change
slope_stdev.description: Change in slope across the parcel (standard deviation)

noise_mean.name: Noise
noise_mean.description: Mean noise level across the parcel (in decibels)

noise_max.name: Noise (max)
noise_max.description: Maximum noise level at any pat of the parcel (in decibels)

osm_street_speed_limit.name: Street speed limit
osm_street_speed_limit.description: Street speed limit (from Open Street Map)

osm_street_lanes.name: Street lanes
osm_street_lanes.description: Number of lanes on the street (from Open Street Map)

osm_corner_lot_type.name: Corner lot type
osm_corner_lot_type.description: Type of corner lot (from Open Street Map)

osm_is_corner_lot.name: Is corner lot
osm_is_corner_lot.description: Whether the parcel is a corner lot (from Open Street Map)

osm_corner_lot_street.name: Corner lot street
osm_corner_lot_street.description: Street of the corner lot (from Open Street Map)

osm_is_cul_de_sac.name: Is cul-de-sac
osm_is_cul_de_sac.description: Whether the parcel is on a cul-de-sac (from Open Street Map)

osm_waterfront_name.name: Waterfront name
osm_waterfront_name.description: Name of the waterfront (from Open Street Map)

osm_is_waterfront.name: Is waterfront
osm_is_waterfront.description: Whether the parcel is on the waterfront (from Open Street Map)

osm_golf_course_name.name: Golf course name
osm_golf_course_name.description: Name of the golf course (from Open Street Map)

osm_on_golf_course.name: On golf course
osm_on_golf_course.description: Whether the parcel is on a golf course (from Open Street Map)

osm_park_name.name: Park name
osm_park_name.description: Name of the park (from Open Street Map)

osm_on_park.name: On park
osm_on_park.description: Whether the parcel is on a park (from Open Street Map)

latitude_norm.name: Northerliness
latitude_norm.description: The percentage of the distance from the southernmost point to the northernmost point in the jurisdiction, with 100% being the northernmost point

longitude_norm.name: Easterliness
longitude_norm.description: The percentage of the distance from the westernmost point to the easternmost point in the jurisdiction, with 100% being the easternmost point

is_vacant.name: Is vacant
is_vacant.description: Whether the parcel is vacant (no building is present)

potential_vacant_sale.name: Potential vacant sale
potential_vacant_sale.description: Whether the auto-detector flagged the parcel as potentially vacant at time of sale

valid_for_ratio_study.name: Valid for ratio study
valid_for_ratio_study.description: Whether the parcel is valid for a ratio study (e.g. the sale is valid and the parcel has not changed significantly since the sale)

valid_for_land_ratio_study.name: Valid for land ratio study
valid_for_land_ratio_study.description: Whether the parcel is valid for a land ratio study (e.g. the sale is valid, and only the land value will be used int he study)

valid_for_modeling.name: Valid for modeling
valid_for_modeling.description: Whether the parcel is valid for modeling (e.g. the sale is valid and we know what the parcel looked like at time of sale)

warning_vacant_discrepancy.name: Vacant discrepancy warning
warning_vacant_discrepancy.description: Whether there is a discrepancy in characteristics indicating whether the parcel is currently vacant or improved

warning_vacant_positive_year_built.name: Vacant discrepancy: positive year built
warning_vacant_positive_year_built.description: If true, the parcel has a year built (indicating a building), yet the parcel is listed as vacant

warning_vacant_positive_impr_numeric.name: Vacant discrepancy: numeric improvement
warning_vacant_positive_impr_numeric.description: If true, the parcel has a non-zero improvement value such as finished square feet (indicating a building), yet the parcel is listed as vacant

warning_vacant_has_impr_categorical.name: Vacant discrepancy: categorical improvement
warning_vacant_has_impr_categorical.description: If true, the parcel has a non-null improvement description such as building type (indicating a building), yet the parcel is listed as vacant

sale_price_land_sqft.name: Sale price per land square foot
sale_price_land_sqft.description: Sale price divided by the size of the parcel

sale_price_impr_sqft.name: Sale price per improvement square foot
sale_price_impr_sqft.description: Sale price divided by the size of the improvement

sale_price_time_adj.name: Sale price (time adjusted)
sale_price_time_adj.description: Sale price adjusted for property inflation, as of the valuation date

sale_price_time_adj_land_sqft.name: Sale price (time adjusted) per land square foot
sale_price_time_adj_land_sqft.description: Time-adjusted sale price divided by the size of the parcel

sale_price_time_adj_impr_sqft.name: Sale price (time adjusted) per improvement square foot
sale_price_time_adj_impr_sqft.description: Time-adjusted sale price divided by the size of the improvement

deed_grantor.name: Deed grantor
deed_grantor.description: Name of the person or entity granting the deed

deed_grantee.name: Deed grantee
deed_grantee.description: Name of the person or entity receiving the deed

sale_age_days.name: Sale age (days)
sale_age_days.description: Number of days that have transpired between the date of sale and the valuation date

spatial_lag_sale_price.name: Local price trend
spatial_lag_sale_price.description: Weighted average of nearby sale prices

spatial_lag_sale_price_vacant.name: Local vacant lot price trend
spatial_lag_sale_price_vacant.description: Weighted average of nearby vacant lot sale prices

spatial_lag_sale_price_time_adj.name: Local price trend (time-adjusted)
spatial_lag_sale_price_time_adj.description: Weighted average of nearby time-adjusted sale prices

spatial_lag_sale_price_land_sqft.name: Local vacant lot $/land sqft trend
spatial_lag_sale_price_land_sqft.description: Weighted average of nearby vacant lot sale prices on a per land sqft basis

spatial_lag_sale_price_impr_sqft.name: Local $/impr sqft trend
spatial_lag_sale_price_impr_sqft.description: Weighted average of nearby sale prices on a per sqft basis

spatial_lag_sale_price_time_adj_land_sqf.name: Local vacant lot $/land sqft trend (time-adjusted)
spatial_lag_sale_price_time_adj_land_sqf.description: Weighted average of nearby time-adjusted sale prices on a per land sqft basis

spatial_lag_sale_price_time_adj_impr_sqf.name: Local $/impr sqft trend (time-adjusted)
spatial_lag_sale_price_time_adj_impr_sqf.description: Weighted average of nearby time-adjusted sale prices on a per sqft basis
